# Runs each time STA connects to upstream network (NET_EV_UPSTREAM_UP) — on a
# temp task, ok to block. AP-only mode does not trigger this.
#
# Spangap default: just block until NTP gives us a sane wall clock. Apps that
# enable OTA should override this file in their own data/factory_state/net_up
# to add `version` (auto-check for new firmware on each upstream-up).
date wait 60
